  2024,"04",/general-conference/2024/04/53stevenson,Por el élder Gary E. Stevenson,46,"Mosíah 2:41."
  2024,"04",/general-conference/2024/04/53stevenson,Por el élder Gary E. Stevenson,47,"Mateo 22:39."
